handy n/w cmds 
  ip link - list and modify interfaces on the host.
  ip addr - to see the ip addresses assigned to those interaces.
  ip addr add - is used to set ip address on the interfaces (valid till upto restart)
  ip route/route - see the routing table
  tp route add - to add in routing table.

  nslookup  - to query a hostname from DNS server
  dig       - to test dns name resolution